    <h1>Media contact line</h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <h3>For editor only</h3><strong>Beginning on Monday, 12 February, the Ministry of Fisheries and Coastal Affairs will staff a media contact line during working hours. The press must exclusively use the telephone number +47 22 24 66 99 between 8.00 and 15.45 on weekdays. </strong>
<h4></h4>
<p class="MsoNormal">If there is a particular need for contact outside of working hours, the press contacts may be reached on their mobile numbers.</p>
<ul>
<li>
<div class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;<a href="/en/dep/fkd/The-Ministry-of-Fisheries-and-Coastal-Affairs/organisation/Departments/department-of-information-and-communicat.html?id=85853">Press contacts</a></div></li></ul>
  </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
